# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]
### Added
- Support for mutual exclusion between behaviors.
- Support for finite behaviors.
- Behaviours programming style seems like [JADE](https://jade.tilab.com/).
- Support for paralell execution of behaviors (default execution method).
- Support for sequential execution of behaviors.
- Message reading in the blocking and non-blocking modes.
- Message delivery made by AID objects instead of local names.
- Support for postpone the message delivery (5 min by default). It is useful when the AMS
is not available at the system initiation.
- Addition of more fields (ontology and language) in the message filtering system.

## [x.x.x] - 2020-05-26
### Added
- All the previous version of PADE.